text: Anna Sofía Sevdal Jakobsen (born 20 December 1993), known as Ansy Sevdal, is a Faroese football midfielder who currently plays for EB/Streymur/Skála and the Faroe Islands women's national football team. == Personal life == She is the younger sister of fellow Faroese international Heidi Sevdal. == Honours == EB/Streymur/Skála *1. deild kvinnur: 2017, 2018 *Steypakappingin kvinnur: 2017, 2018 == References == Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Faroese women's footballers Category:Faroe Islands women's international footballers Category:Women's association football midfielders
